@startuml
title Attendance System Overview
left to right direction
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam packageStyle rectangle

actor Employee
actor "Kiosk Terminal" as Kiosk
actor "AI Service" as AI

rectangle "Attendance System" {
  usecase "Face Registration" as UC_FaceReg
  usecase "Face Recognition" as UC_FaceRecog
  usecase "Check In / Check Out" as UC_Attendance
  usecase "Attendance Log Sync" as UC_Sync
}

Employee --> UC_FaceReg
Employee --> UC_Attendance

Kiosk --> UC_FaceReg
Kiosk --> UC_FaceRecog
Kiosk --> UC_Attendance
Kiosk --> UC_Sync

AI --> UC_FaceReg
AI --> UC_FaceRecog

note right of UC_FaceReg
Detailed diagrams in:
 - 03-usecase-face-recognition.puml
 - 04-activity-face-enrollment.puml
 - 05-sequence-face-enrollment.puml
end note

note right of UC_Attendance
Detailed diagrams in:
 - 03-usecase-attendance-management.puml
 - 04-activity-check-in.puml
 - 05-sequence-check-in.puml
end note

@enduml
